	"description": "Keephub integration node for n8n workflow automation",
	"longDescription": "Keephub is your AI-powered frontline employee platform. Connect teams across communication, scheduling, HR admin, tasks, and auditsâ€”all from one hub. With n8n, automate workflows that sync schedules, trigger HR actions, coordinate communications, and manage tasks across your entire tech stack.",
	"license": "MIT",
	"keywords": [
		"n8n-community-node-package",
		"keephub",
		"employee-engagement",
		"frontline-workers",
		"deskless-workers",
